# Sensor Registry

Status: draft

REVIEW REQUIRED: confirm owner, source, purpose, retirement condition, and
review cadence before relying on these sensors for completion, release, or
maintenance decisions.

This registry records the checks and signals agents and humans use to decide
whether work is ready. HarnessForge can seed detected commands, but the target
project owns the meaning and lifecycle of each sensor.

